SeleniumLog.Net 3.2.0
.NET test automation logging framework which can output in simple text format (viewable in any text editor) or rich text format viewable using SeleniumLog Viewer(seleniumlog.com). It has fully compatible interface with Log4Net.
releaseNotes:
- Compatible with Log4Net user interface (ie., log.Info, log.Warning, log.Debug, log.Error, log.Fatal) 
- Supports both Normal (full page) and Ultra-fast (visible section) screenshots 
- Fixed slAssert library
